com.radirius.mercury.utilities.logging
Class Logger

java.lang.Object
  com.radirius.mercury.utilities.logging.Logger

public class Logger
extends java.lang.Object

A class that will log in different levels of impact, from NULL to SEVERE. SEVERE being the program killer.

Author:
wessles, Jeviny
